episodes.title: Prince Andrew stripped of all titles and lease to royal home by King Charles | HELLO!
episodes.description:
Buckingham Palace has confirmed the King has taken action to formally remove Prince Andrew's titles, giving him a new surname instead. The palace has also confirmed that the former Duke of York will vacate his Windsor home, Royal Lodge. So, what is Andrew's new name and where has it come from?
